During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Nordoxicon/Legends|Nordoxicon's]] ''' Micro Instrument division''' was responsible for the creation of the bomb sights that were fitted aboard [[Sienar Fleet Systems/Legends|Sienar Fleet Systems]]' [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|TIE/sa bomber]]. The sight was reportedly so accurate that [[Bomber/Legends|bomber]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] were able to place a free-falling [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonator]] through the top hatch of a [[Laser/Legends|laser]] turret from a distance of ten [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] while flying through a hurricane.

